g.text: Note: IO32 and IO33 might be internally
connected to 32kHz crystal. IO0, IO2 and IO5
are boot mode pins. IO12-IO15 are JTAG.
IO0 high/floating: Normal, pull low: Serial bootloader.
Connect to DTR. Connect EN to RTS.
IO12 pull high: 1.8V. IO15 pull low: Mute boot messages.
